   <talk_paragraph index="n087_beggar-accepting" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n087_beggar-accepting-a" mid="7" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html> What happened in Lotus Marsh? </html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n087_beggar-accepting-b" mid="8" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html> What's Lotus Marsh like? </html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n087_beggar-accepting-c" mid="9" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html> Why did you go to Lotus Marsh? </html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n087_beggar-accepting-d" mid="10" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html> Have you really been to Lotus Marsh? </html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="5"><![CDATA[<html>$Loffy the Beggar$<BR>Oh, good. Now you are asking me about some good questions. But that doesn't mean you are not stupid anymore. I've travelled many places. Lotus Marsh, Telnumara and Anu Arendel. That reminds me of the horrible swamp of Lotus Marsh.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n087_beggar-accepting-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Loffy the Beggar$<BR>I wasted my time because of the false information from stupid Smith. The place where huge treasures were suppose to be were full of mud and there was a old piece of paper. All that effort for a piece of paper! That paper screwed me over! <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Loffy grinds his teeth)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n087_beggar-accepting-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Loffy the Beggar$<BR>
I've told you, it's all swamp. And those rivers are darn narrow. I had to leave my boat and go up-stream with a little paddle boat. The worst was the natives. They hate people from the Northern Kingdom. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n087_beggar-accepting-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Loffy the Beggar$<BR>That's all to find a treasure! Stupid Smith told me there was a big treasure but all there were, were mud holes and a useless piece of paper. Darn paper! </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n087_beggar-accepting-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Loffy the Beggar$<BR>Huh, after all that you don't trust me? I can't do anything then. Go away! I don't want to talk to someone who doesn't trust me. BowBowBoW!! </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
